  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "コスモタンクは、宇宙の戦車バトルゲームです。あなたは戦車「タイガー a-1」の指揮官となり、マスターインセクトとその手下たちに対して、陸上と宇宙で戦う任務を担います。ゲームには、上から見下ろす視点のレベルと、自由に動き回れる一人称視点のレベルが用意されています。設定には、開放的な屋外環境、洞窟、そして宇宙が含まれています。進行するにつれて、砲撃力を高め、より多くの攻撃に耐えられるように、ゆっくりと砲身や装甲をアップグレードしていきましょう。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The player controls an armoured fighting vehicle from either a first-person perspective or a third-person perspective; depending on the level design. All games begin on a planet's surface with an overhead view. When the player enters a tunnel, the view switches to first-person. After destroying the Life Core inside a tunnel, the player travels to a new planet through a vertically scrolling stage.\n\nCosmo Tank has three modes. In quest mode, the object of the game is to destroy Alien Life Cores on five planets to free them from Master Insect. Players can earn experience levels in the quest mode by defeating enemies. The maximum amount of experience points that a player can earn is 999; which allows players to reach the level cap of 6. In training mode, the player practices in a closed area and is given a ranking. In vs. mode, the Game Link Cable is used to allow two players to race to defeat the alien leader.\n\nAfter either beating the game or acquiring a game over, the player is given a rank that shows how far he made it in the game along with his target score. The lowest rank in the game is a skull and crossbones (signifying a casualty on the battlefield).",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
